  <diagram name="Sequence Diagram" id="XRHTEFdg30vu3tCoWi3h">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1571" dy="1039" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="vCbULJYbUddzt6d0eydb-0" />
        <mxCell id="vCbULJYbUddzt6d0eydb-1" parent="vCbULJYbUddzt6d0eydb-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\ntitle Self-Healing System - Sequence Diagram\n\nactor \&quot;System Admin\&quot; as Admin\nparticipant \&quot;Prometheus\&quot; as Prom\nparticipant \&quot;MonitoringService\\n(Analyzer)\&quot; as Monitor\nparticipant \&quot;TaskApi\&quot; as API\nparticipant \&quot;Anomaly Rules\\n(Memory/CPU/Error)\&quot; as Rules\nparticipant \&quot;RemediationEngine\&quot; as Remed\nparticipant \&quot;DiagnosticService\&quot; as Diag\nparticipant \&quot;LearningService\&quot; as Learn\nparticipant \&quot;KubernetesScaler\&quot; as K8s\nparticipant \&quot;NotificationService\&quot; as Notify\n\n== Monitoring Loop (every 5 seconds) ==\n\nMonitor -&gt; Prom : Query 4 metrics in parallel\\n(memory, CPU, error rate, request rate)\nactivate Monitor\nProm --&gt; Monitor : Metric values\n\nMonitor -&gt; API : POST /api/metrics (store records)\nAPI --&gt; Monitor : Stored\n\nMonitor -&gt; Rules : Evaluate sliding-window rules\nactivate Rules\nRules --&gt; Monitor : FailureEvent (if anomaly detected)\ndeactivate Rules\n\n== Self-Healing Pipeline (triggered on anomaly) ==\n\nMonitor -&gt; Remed : HandleFailureAsync(failureEvent)\nactivate Remed\n\nRemed -&gt; API : POST /api/failureevents\\n(persist failure)\nAPI --&gt; Remed : FailureEvent with Id\n\nRemed -&gt; Diag : DiagnoseAsync(failure)\nactivate Diag\nDiag -&gt; Prom : Query all 4 metrics (parallel)\nProm --&gt; Diag : Current metric values\nDiag -&gt; Diag : Correlate signals\\n(classify root cause)\nDiag --&gt; Remed : Diagnosis\\n(rootCause, severity, confidence, signals)\ndeactivate Diag\n\nRemed -&gt; Learn : GetBestStrategy(rootCause)\nactivate Learn\nLearn --&gt; Remed : StrategyRecommendation (or null)\ndeactivate Learn\n\nnote right of Remed\n  Select multi-step strategy\n  based on root cause + learning history\n  (e.g. RestartWithBuffer: ScaleUp → RestartPod)\nend note\n\nloop For each step in strategy\n    Remed -&gt; API : POST /api/recoveryactions\\n(create action record)\n    API --&gt; Remed : RecoveryAction with Id\n\n    Remed -&gt; K8s : Execute step (ScaleUp / RestartPod)\n    activate K8s\n    K8s --&gt; Remed : ScaleResult (success/fail)\n    deactivate K8s\n\n    Remed -&gt; API : PATCH /api/recoveryactions/{id}/status\n    API --&gt; Remed : Updated\nend\n\nRemed -&gt; API : PATCH /api/failureevents/{id}/resolve\nAPI --&gt; Remed : Resolved\n\nRemed -&gt; Learn : RecordOutcome(rootCause, strategy, success)\nLearn --&gt; Remed : Recorded (updates success rates)\n\nRemed -&gt; Notify : NotifyAsync(failure, strategy, status, details)\nactivate Notify\nNotify --&gt; Admin : Console log + webhook notification\ndeactivate Notify\n\ndeactivate Remed\ndeactivate Monitor\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="zuUWt1xrokjTNzg8qlEW-0">
          <mxCell parent="vCbULJYbUddzt6d0eydb-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="1255" width="1786" x="210" y="280" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="USE Case Diagram" id="bK0BsJEalD1F1U_FXoFY">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1664" dy="1100" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="VMxZ2fkhidbx1vGB3dwL-0" />
        <mxCell id="VMxZ2fkhidbx1vGB3dwL-1" parent="VMxZ2fkhidbx1vGB3dwL-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\nleft to right direction\ntitle Use Case Diagram – Self-Healing System\n\nactor \&quot;System Admin\&quot; as Admin\nactor \&quot;Prometheus\&quot; as Prom &lt;&lt;system&gt;&gt;\nactor \&quot;Kubernetes API\&quot; as K8s &lt;&lt;system&gt;&gt;\n\nrectangle \&quot;Self-Healing System\&quot; {\n\n  &#39; ── Observability ──\n  package \&quot;Metric Collection\&quot; {\n    usecase \&quot;Pull Metrics from Prometheus\\n(memory, CPU, error rate, request rate)\&quot; as UC1\n    usecase \&quot;Store Metrics in PostgreSQL\&quot; as UC2\n  }\n\n  &#39; ── Anomaly Detection ──\n  package \&quot;Anomaly Detection\&quot; {\n    usecase \&quot;Detect Anomaly\\n(sliding-window rules)\&quot; as UC3\n    usecase \&quot;Detect Memory Leak\\n(OLS regression, R² gating)\&quot; as UC3a\n    usecase \&quot;Detect CPU Spike\\n(7/10 samples &gt; 80%)\&quot; as UC3b\n    usecase \&quot;Detect High Error Rate\\n(4/6 samples &gt; 10%)\&quot; as UC3c\n  }\n\n  &#39; ── Diagnosis ──\n  package \&quot;Root Cause Diagnosis\&quot; {\n    usecase \&quot;Diagnose Root Cause\\n(correlate 4 signals)\&quot; as UC4\n    usecase \&quot;Classify Failure Type\\n(ResourceExhaustion, TrafficOverload,\\nApplicationError, DependencyFailure,\\nMemoryLeakSuspected, HighCpuUsage)\&quot; as UC5\n  }\n\n  &#39; ── Remediation ──\n  package \&quot;Remediation\&quot; {\n    usecase \&quot;Select Recovery Strategy\\n(learning-informed)\&quot; as UC6\n    usecase \&quot;Execute Multi-Step Recovery\&quot; as UC7\n    usecase \&quot;Restart Pod\\n(rolling restart via annotation patch)\&quot; as UC8\n    usecase \&quot;Scale Deployment\\n(adjust replica count)\&quot; as UC9\n    usecase \&quot;Persist Failure Event\&quot; as UC10\n    usecase \&quot;Persist Recovery Action\&quot; as UC11\n  }\n\n  &#39; ── Learning ──\n  package \&quot;Learning Loop\&quot; {\n    usecase \&quot;Record Recovery Outcome\\n(success/failure per strategy)\&quot; as UC12\n    usecase \&quot;Recommend Best Strategy\\n(historical success rate &gt; 70%)\&quot; as UC13\n  }\n\n  &#39; ── Notification ──\n  package \&quot;Notification\&quot; {\n    usecase \&quot;Send Alert Notification\\n(console log + webhook)\&quot; as UC14\n  }\n\n  &#39; ── Dashboard &amp; Stress Testing ──\n  package \&quot;Dashboard &amp; Testing\&quot; {\n    usecase \&quot;View System Health Dashboard\\n(metrics, failures, recoveries)\&quot; as UC15\n    usecase \&quot;Trigger Stress Test\\n(memory leak / CPU exhaustion)\&quot; as UC16\n    usecase \&quot;View Learning Report\&quot; as UC17\n  }\n}\n\n&#39; ── Actor Associations ──\nProm -- UC1\nK8s -- UC8\nK8s -- UC9\nAdmin -- UC15\nAdmin -- UC16\nAdmin -- UC17\nAdmin -- UC14\n\n&#39; ── Relationships ──\n\n&#39; Metric collection\nUC1 .&gt; UC2 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Anomaly detection extends\nUC3 &lt;. UC3a : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\nUC3 &lt;. UC3b : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\nUC3 &lt;. UC3c : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Detection triggers diagnosis\nUC3 .&gt; UC4 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\nUC4 .&gt; UC5 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Diagnosis triggers remediation\nUC4 ..&gt; UC6 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\nUC6 .&gt; UC13 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\nUC6 .&gt; UC7 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Recovery execution\nUC7 .&gt; UC10 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\nUC7 .&gt; UC11 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\nUC7 .&gt; UC8 : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\nUC7 .&gt; UC9 : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n&#39; Post-recovery\nUC7 .&gt; UC12 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\nUC7 .&gt; UC14 : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="u3OTkACgM1WuUWjRRFq6-1">
          <mxCell parent="VMxZ2fkhidbx1vGB3dwL-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="1426" width="1022" x="20" y="20" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="UML ACTIVITY DIAGRAM" id="HGJrefXZtosmaXHtcZIr">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1359" dy="895" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="gjdCnUy1hkRAEtWcRdec-0" />
        <mxCell id="gjdCnUy1hkRAEtWcRdec-1" parent="gjdCnUy1hkRAEtWcRdec-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam activity {\n  BackgroundColor white\n  BorderColor black\n}\n\nstart\n\n:Collect Pod Metrics;\n\nif (Pod Healthy?) then (Yes)\n  :Continue Monitoring;\nelse (No)\n  :Detect Failure;\n  :Analyze Failure Cause;\n\n  if (Policy Available?) then (Yes)\n    :Select Healing Action;\n\n    fork\n      :Restart Pod;\n    fork again\n      :Reschedule Pod;\n    fork again\n      :Auto Scale Resources;\n    end fork\n\n    :Send Alert;\n    :Update Logs &amp; Audit Trail;\n  else (No)\n    :Notify Admin;\n  endif\nendif\n\nstop\n@enduml\n&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="gjdCnUy1hkRAEtWcRdec-2">
          <mxCell parent="gjdCnUy1hkRAEtWcRdec-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="632" width="682" x="20" y="20" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="  ACTIVITY OF Monitoring Process" id="GFPY3MWVFvl1FiFbkgBL">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1414" dy="935" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="NYdGZaHX4RRDeWI_MojX-0" />
        <mxCell id="NYdGZaHX4RRDeWI_MojX-1" parent="NYdGZaHX4RRDeWI_MojX-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\ntitle Activity 1: Metric Collection (every 5 seconds)\n\nparticipant \&quot;MonitoringService\\n(Analyzer)\&quot; as Monitor\nparticipant \&quot;Prometheus\&quot; as Prom\nparticipant \&quot;TaskApi\&quot; as API\n\nMonitor -&gt; Prom : GET memory (system_runtime_working_set)\nMonitor -&gt; Prom : GET CPU (rate(process_cpu_seconds_total))\nMonitor -&gt; Prom : GET error rate (5xx / total)\nMonitor -&gt; Prom : GET request rate (http_requests_received_total)\nnote right of Monitor: All 4 queries run in parallel\n\nProm --&gt; Monitor : memory samples\nProm --&gt; Monitor : CPU percent\nProm --&gt; Monitor : error rate percent\nProm --&gt; Monitor : request rate/sec\n\nMonitor -&gt; API : POST /api/metrics\\n(batch of MetricRecordDto)\nAPI --&gt; Monitor : Stored\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="NYdGZaHX4RRDeWI_MojX-2">
          <mxCell parent="NYdGZaHX4RRDeWI_MojX-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="481" width="522" x="105" y="160" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="ACTIVITY OF Failure Detection &amp; Analysis" id="qKTuytV0Jm0JZxkq5a5x">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1414" dy="935" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="NxhWfaPaIzOU_YdydVPu-0" />
        <mxCell id="NxhWfaPaIzOU_YdydVPu-1" parent="NxhWfaPaIzOU_YdydVPu-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\ntitle Activity 2: Anomaly Detection (sliding-window rules)\n\nparticipant \&quot;MonitoringService\&quot; as Monitor\nparticipant \&quot;MemoryLeakRule\&quot; as Mem\nparticipant \&quot;CpuSpikeRule\&quot; as Cpu\nparticipant \&quot;HighErrorRateRule\&quot; as Err\n\nMonitor -&gt; Mem : Evaluate(latestMemoryValue)\nactivate Mem\nnote right of Mem\n  20-sample OLS regression\n  Trigger: slope &gt; 15 MB/min AND R² &gt; 0.60\n  Cooldown: 3 minutes\nend note\nMem --&gt; Monitor : FailureEvent or null\ndeactivate Mem\n\nMonitor -&gt; Cpu : Evaluate(cpuPercent)\nactivate Cpu\nnote right of Cpu\n  10-sample window\n  Trigger: 7/10 samples &gt; 80%\n  Cooldown: 5 minutes\nend note\nCpu --&gt; Monitor : FailureEvent or null\ndeactivate Cpu\n\nMonitor -&gt; Err : Evaluate(errorRate)\nactivate Err\nnote right of Err\n  6-sample window\n  Trigger: 4/6 samples &gt; 10%\n  Cooldown: 3 minutes\nend note\nErr --&gt; Monitor : FailureEvent or null\ndeactivate Err\n\nalt Anomaly detected\n    Monitor -&gt; Monitor : TriggerRecoveryAsync(failureEvent)\n    note right: Proceeds to Activity 3\nend\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="NxhWfaPaIzOU_YdydVPu-2">
          <mxCell parent="NxhWfaPaIzOU_YdydVPu-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="548" width="769" x="105" y="160" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="ACTIVITY OFHealing &amp; Recovery Process" id="qY9XEFUkd5pIdUE-9G6K">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1414" dy="935" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="1IMR60aIZkzyypzyw79I-0" />
        <mxCell id="1IMR60aIZkzyypzyw79I-1" parent="1IMR60aIZkzyypzyw79I-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\ntitle Activity 3: Failure Persistence &amp; Root Cause Diagnosis\n\nparticipant \&quot;RemediationEngine\&quot; as Remed\nparticipant \&quot;TaskApi\&quot; as API\nparticipant \&quot;DiagnosticService\&quot; as Diag\nparticipant \&quot;Prometheus\&quot; as Prom\n\nRemed -&gt; API : POST /api/failureevents\\n(persist FailureEvent)\nactivate API\nAPI --&gt; Remed : FailureEvent { Id = guid }\ndeactivate API\n\nRemed -&gt; Diag : DiagnoseAsync(failure)\nactivate Diag\n\nDiag -&gt; Prom : GET memory samples\nDiag -&gt; Prom : GET CPU percent\nDiag -&gt; Prom : GET error rate\nDiag -&gt; Prom : GET request rate\nnote right of Diag: All 4 queries in parallel\n\nProm --&gt; Diag : metric values\n\nDiag -&gt; Diag : CorrelateSignals()\nnote right of Diag\n  Signal correlation logic:\n  - HighMemory + HighCPU + !HighTraffic → ResourceExhaustion\n  - HighTraffic + HighErrors + HighCPU   → TrafficOverload\n  - HighErrors + !HighTraffic            → ApplicationError\n  - HighTraffic + HighErrors + !HighCPU  → DependencyFailure\n  - HighMemory only                      → MemoryLeakSuspected\n  - HighCPU only                         → HighCpuUsage\nend note\n\nDiag --&gt; Remed : Diagnosis\\n(rootCause, severity, confidence, correlatedSignals)\ndeactivate Diag\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="1IMR60aIZkzyypzyw79I-2">
          <mxCell parent="1IMR60aIZkzyypzyw79I-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="596" width="866" x="105" y="160" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="Copy of ACTIVITY OFHealing &amp; Recovery Process" id="Fh-gi0Lz7Oe9mJcoB1qK">
    <mxGraphModel dx="943" dy="623" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="FNOmV2pi9qmE1oXPofee-0" />
        <mxCell id="FNOmV2pi9qmE1oXPofee-1" parent="FNOmV2pi9qmE1oXPofee-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\ntitle Activity 4: Strategy Selection (Learning-Informed)\n\nparticipant \&quot;RemediationEngine\&quot; as Remed\nparticipant \&quot;LearningService\&quot; as Learn\n\nRemed -&gt; Learn : GetBestStrategy(rootCause)\nactivate Learn\n\nalt Has history for rootCause\n    Learn --&gt; Remed : StrategyRecommendation\\n(strategyName, successRate, totalAttempts)\nelse No history\n    Learn --&gt; Remed : null\nend\ndeactivate Learn\n\nalt Learned strategy: successRate &gt; 70% AND attempts &gt;= 3\n    Remed -&gt; Remed : Use learned strategy\nelse Default strategy by root cause\n    Remed -&gt; Remed : Select default strategy\n    note right of Remed\n      ResourceExhaustion  → RestartAndScale (RestartPod → ScaleUp)\n      TrafficOverload     → ScaleUpAggressive (ScaleUp)\n      ApplicationError    → RestartAndMonitor (RestartPod)\n      DependencyFailure   → ScaleAndRestart (ScaleUp → RestartPod)\n      MemoryLeakSuspected → RestartWithBuffer (ScaleUp → RestartPod)\n      HighCpuUsage        → ScaleUpForCpu (ScaleUp)\n    end note\nend\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="FNOmV2pi9qmE1oXPofee-2">
          <mxCell parent="FNOmV2pi9qmE1oXPofee-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="495" width="532" x="105" y="160" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="Copy of Copy of ACTIVITY OFHealing &amp; Recovery Process" id="efcO19xBEnSlTGbN4s7r">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1414" dy="935" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="xpO2YET9USj3fGInb1u7-0" />
        <mxCell id="xpO2YET9USj3fGInb1u7-1" parent="xpO2YET9USj3fGInb1u7-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\ntitle Activity 5: Recovery Execution (Multi-Step Strategy)\n\nparticipant \&quot;RemediationEngine\&quot; as Remed\nparticipant \&quot;TaskApi\&quot; as API\nparticipant \&quot;KubernetesScaler\&quot; as K8s\n\nloop For each step in strategy.Steps\n\n    Remed -&gt; API : POST /api/recoveryactions\\n{ failureEventId, actionType, target, status=\&quot;InProgress\&quot; }\n    API --&gt; Remed : RecoveryAction { Id = guid }\n\n    alt step.Action == \&quot;ScaleUp\&quot;\n        Remed -&gt; K8s : ScaleDeploymentAsync(deployment, replicas)\n        activate K8s\n        K8s -&gt; K8s : PATCH deployment scale\n        K8s --&gt; Remed : ScaleResult\n        deactivate K8s\n    else step.Action == \&quot;RestartPod\&quot;\n        Remed -&gt; K8s : RestartDeploymentAsync(deployment)\n        activate K8s\n        K8s -&gt; K8s : PATCH pod template annotation\\n(triggers rolling restart)\n        K8s --&gt; Remed : ScaleResult\n        deactivate K8s\n    end\n\n    Remed -&gt; API : PATCH /api/recoveryactions/{id}/status\\n{ status=\&quot;Success\&quot;|\&quot;Failed\&quot;, details }\n    API --&gt; Remed : Updated\n\n    alt Step failed AND !ContinueOnFailure\n        Remed -&gt; Remed : Abort strategy\n        note right: Remaining steps skipped\n    else Step succeeded or ContinueOnFailure\n        opt step.DelayAfterMs &gt; 0\n            Remed -&gt; Remed : Wait(delayAfterMs)\n        end\n    end\n\nend\n\nalt Overall success\n    Remed -&gt; API : PATCH /api/failureevents/{id}/resolve\n    API --&gt; Remed : Resolved\nend\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="xpO2YET9USj3fGInb1u7-2">
          <mxCell parent="xpO2YET9USj3fGInb1u7-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="786" width="857" x="105" y="160" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="Copy of Copy of Copy of ACTIVITY OFHealing &amp; Recovery Process" id="BWdZIGsVxra_hmx_RMWO">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1414" dy="935" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="KsPB2FWAnqU1EfCqzl0h-0" />
        <mxCell id="KsPB2FWAnqU1EfCqzl0h-1" parent="KsPB2FWAnqU1EfCqzl0h-0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\ntitle Activity 6: Outcome Recording &amp; Notification\n\nactor \&quot;System Admin\&quot; as Admin\nparticipant \&quot;RemediationEngine\&quot; as Remed\nparticipant \&quot;LearningService\&quot; as Learn\nparticipant \&quot;NotificationService\&quot; as Notify\n\nRemed -&gt; Learn : RecordOutcome(rootCause, strategyName, success)\nactivate Learn\nLearn -&gt; Learn : Update success/failure counters\\n(ConcurrentDictionary)\nLearn -&gt; Learn : Enqueue LearningEvent\\n(for API/dashboard)\nnote right of Learn\n  Logs: \&quot;ResourceExhaustion + RestartWithBuffer → SUCCESS\n  (success rate: 83%, total: 6)\&quot;\nend note\nLearn --&gt; Remed : Recorded\ndeactivate Learn\n\nRemed -&gt; Notify : NotifyAsync(failure, strategyName, status, details)\nactivate Notify\nNotify -&gt; Notify : Log to console\\n\&quot; [ALERT] MemoryLeakSuspected...\&quot;\nNotify -&gt; Notify : Log structured message\n\nalt Webhook URL configured\n    Notify -&gt; Admin : POST webhook\\n{ failureType, severity, recoveryAction,\\n  recoveryStatus, details, timestamp }\nelse No webhook\n    Notify -&gt; Notify : Log \&quot;notification logged only\&quot;\nend\ndeactivate Notify\n\n@enduml&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="KsPB2FWAnqU1EfCqzl0h-2">
          <mxCell parent="KsPB2FWAnqU1EfCqzl0h-1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="692" width="987" x="246" y="152" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
