        <mxCell id="lwDhFy6XJbLUevfUC_to-24" parent="lwDhFy6XJbLUevfUC_to-1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;spacing=0;horizontal=1;textShadow=0;autosizeText=1;imageAspect=1;resizeWidth=0;autosize=0;fontSize=15;" value="• Runtime environment is highly dynamic due to automatic scaling&lt;br&gt;• Pods may restart or reschedule across cluster nodes&lt;br&gt;• Monitoring load increases during stress testing&lt;br&gt;• Real-time observability is required during anomaly detection&lt;br&gt;• Local development environment differs from production cluster behavior" vertex="1">
