        <mxCell id="dvIYzwfbgYlH83zcDWOg-23" parent="dvIYzwfbgYlH83zcDWOg-1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;spacing=0;horizontal=1;textShadow=0;autosizeText=1;imageAspect=1;resizeWidth=0;autosize=0;fontSize=15;" value="• Metric scraping occurs every 5 seconds through HTTP communication&lt;br&gt;• Analyzer interacts with Prometheus using PromQL queries&lt;br&gt;• Kubernetes receives restart and scaling commands programmatically&lt;br&gt;• Recovery status is pushed back into the system database&lt;br&gt;• UI updates immediately after remediation execution" vertex="1">
